work.work-title: My heart is fixed, eternal God

encoding.software: PDFtoMusic Pro v1.6.5 Build 1B9E7 (c) Myriad - http://www.myriad-online.com

credit.credit-words: Christ for me. He is my Prophet, Priest and King, Who did for me salvation bring; And while I've breath I mean to sing, Christ for me, Christ for me.

In Him I see the Godhead shine; Christ for me, Christ for me; He is the Majesty Divine: Christ for me. The Father's well-beloved Son, Copartner of His royal throne, Who did for human guilt atone, Christ for me, Christ for me.
My heart is fixed, eternal God
Christ for me. And in that all-important day, When I the summons must obey, And pass from this dark world away, Christ for me, Christ for me.
